<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cloud Systems</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: "Segoe UI", system-ui, sans-serif; background: #f8f8f8; color: #1a1a1a; }
    header { background: #0078d4; color: #fff; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
    header h1 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: .02em; }
    header p { font-size: .875rem; opacity: .85; margin-top: .25rem; }
    main { max-width: 860px; margin: 2.5rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    section { background: #fff; border-radius: 4px; padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    section h2 { font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em; color: #0078d4; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    ul { list-style: none; }
    ul li { font-size: .9rem; padding: .3rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; color: #333; }
    ul li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    ul li span { color: #605e5c; font-size: .8rem; float: right; }
    footer { text-align: center; color: #999; font-size: .8rem; padding: 2rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Cloud Systems Infrastructure</h1>
    <p>{{ app_domain }} &mdash; Microsoft Azure, South Central US</p>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section>
      <h2>Infrastructure</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Provisioning <span>Terraform</span></li>
        <li>State backend <span>Azure Blob Storage</span></li>
        <li>Virtual network <span>10.0.0.0/16</span></li>
        <li>App subnet <span>10.0.1.0/24</span></li>
        <li>DB subnet <span>10.0.2.0/24</span></li>
        <li>VMs <span>Ubuntu 24.04 ARM64</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Configuration</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Configuration management <span>Ansible</span></li>
        <li>Secrets management <span>Ansible Vault</span></li>
        <li>Web server <span>nginx</span></li>
        <li>Database <span>MariaDB</span></li>
        <li>DB access <span>appuser@10.0.1.%</span></li>
        <li>DB bind address <span>10.0.2.4</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Security</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>TLS <span>Let's Encrypt</span></li>
        <li>Protocol <span>HTTP/2, TLS 1.2/1.3</span></li>
        <li>HSTS <span>max-age=86400</span></li>
        <li>OCSP stapling <span>enabled</span></li>
        <li>Rate limiting <span>10 req/s</span></li>
        <li>MySQL port 3306 <span>app subnet only</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Access</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>SSH to app VM <span>public IP</span></li>
        <li>SSH to DB VM <span>via bastion</span></li>
        <li>MySQL from internet <span>blocked</span></li>
        <li>SSH source <span>AzureCloud tag</span></li>
        <li>HTTP <span>redirects to HTTPS</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer>Provisioned with Terraform &mdash; Configured with Ansible &mdash; Secured with Let's Encrypt</footer>
</body>
</html>
